### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ✅ Happy path
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/current-user
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
X-Platform: web
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

# ❌ No token
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/current-user
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
X-Platform: web


